    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:24px;">
      <div class="project-meta">Industry: Home Services (HVAC, Plumbing, Flooring, Fencing, Pest Control)</div>
      <h3>Local SEO &amp; Google Business Profile Optimization</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom:14px;"><strong>Challenge:</strong> Improve local search visibility for businesses competing against established local competitors with stronger online presence and historical authority.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:14px;"><strong>Approach:</strong> Audited and optimized Google Business Profiles, improved NAP consistency across business directories, optimized service and location pages around search intent, enhanced internal linking between related services and locations, improved local entity relevance through structured content, and strengthened LocalBusiness schema implementation.</p>
      <p><strong>Tools used:</strong> Google Business Profile, BrightLocal, Google Search Console, Screaming Frog SEO Spider</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:24px;">
      <div class="project-meta">Industry: eCommerce &amp; SaaS</div>
      <h3>Technical SEO Audit &amp; Website Optimization</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom:14px;"><strong>Challenge:</strong> Identify technical issues affecting crawling, rendering, indexing, and website performance that limited organic visibility.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:14px;"><strong>Approach:</strong> Conducted comprehensive technical SEO audits, identified crawl and indexation issues, reviewed canonical implementation, audited XML sitemaps and robots.txt, evaluated JavaScript rendering, validated structured data, and prioritized technical fixes based on impact.</p>
      <p><strong>Tools used:</strong> Screaming Frog SEO Spider, Google Search Console, Google PageSpeed Insights, GTmetrix, Google Rich Results Test</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:24px;">
      <div class="project-meta">Industry: Legal, Finance &amp; Education</div>
      <h3>Semantic SEO &amp; Topical Authority</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom:14px;"><strong>Challenge:</strong> Develop content strategies that improve topical coverage, search intent alignment, and semantic relevance.</p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:14px;"><strong>Approach:</strong> Created topical maps, developed content clusters, identified primary and supporting entities, expanded Entity-Attribute-Verb (EAV) coverage, prepared search-intent-focused content briefs, and designed internal linking strategies to strengthen topical relationships.</p>
      <p><strong>Tools used:</strong> Ahrefs, SEMrush, MarketMuse, SearchAtlas (OTTO SEO)</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h3>Content Strategy &amp; Information Architecture</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom:14px;"><strong>Challenge:</strong> Improve website structure and content organization to reduce topical overlap, strengthen internal linking, and create scalable content ecosystems.</p>
      <p><strong>Approach:</strong> Conducted content audits, identified topical gaps, planned scalable website architecture, organized content clusters, improved contextual internal linking, and structured information hierarchy around user intent.</p>
    </div>
